CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: ProPetro Holding Corp is a Texas-based oilfield services company. It provides hydraulic fracturing and other complementary services to oil and gas companies engaged in the exploration and production of North American unconventional oil and natural gas resources. The company focused is on Permian Basin. The operating segment of the company are Hydraulic Fracturing, Cementing and Coiled Tubing.
